{"tid":1516732,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"612當初堅持還在嗎？那時候你所相信的事 沒有被動搖吧？","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:14:40.000Z","uid":153051,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4718fdb23ee6714de7917e6010347f3542a9a6e7","tid":1516732,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">場運動已經過左幾個月 <br />\n<br />\n相信每一個香港人都經歷過很多 感觸很大<br />\n<br />\n有時候我望住新聞既報導 前線衝緊既勇武 被拉既手足 百感交集</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港人願意企出黎 因為每一個人就係個一點既力量 <br />\n我同自己講 唔好比自己有後悔既機會，<br />\n對比起 曾經代價比我更大既手足<br />\n我呢一點付出算得上係咩 <br />\n我微不足道 但香港係需要每一個人 每一點力量</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>我有個小小既願望<br />\n無論過左幾多個月 發生咩事都好，<br />\n大家都不忘初衷 當初堅持既信念<br />\n一直係心入面 好嗎？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可。<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9c7899eeecc204d663b5df9e6b456ac6408f4d79","tid":1516732,"uid":107199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae53213dfb7fbfc4bb5cf326919977ed1665a65b","tid":1516732,"uid":98926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:10:51.000Z","msg":"831遊行<br />\n831死線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npq7Ds0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpq7Ds0.jpg&h=cd008a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s